%F A064437 a(n) = ceiling((1+sqrt(2))*(n-1)+C) where C = 1/(2+sqrt(2)) = 0.292893218813...
%e A064437 a(6)=13 hence a(13) = a(12) + 3 = 27 + 3 = 30.
